oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Country Music Hall of Fame Volume 2 - Side 1
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: The recording is of a variety of recorded performances. The performances were gathered for the Columbia Special Products: Country Music Hall of Fame Volume 2. The recordings are from an unidentified number of dates and gathered on October 07, 1966. The tape is the first tape of two.
